{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A dark fantasy classic RPG. Customize your race, gender and class. Gather a party with your favorite companions. Change the fate of the characters and the world with your choices. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gameplay </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Create a character.</strong> Customize your race, sex, name, class and non-combat skill. Create a unique protagonist. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Who do you want to venture with?</strong> A human cleric, a dark elf ranger, or an orc defender? Gather a party that's the best for you! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Choices affect the plot.</strong> How you interact with people in neighboring country depends on you, but beware - you may start a war. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Turn-based combat with a focus on teamwork.</strong> Beware classes have their own strengths and weaknesses. Complement each other to win. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Main Characters </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1294380/extras/pCutinDarkLord.png?t=1732503360\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Dark Lord</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The dark-one monarch who has lived for five hundred years. She is determined to end the perennial struggle between dark ones and humans. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1294380/extras/pCutinPrinceOfHeroes.png?t=1732503360\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Hero</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A descendant of the legendary hero. It is a calling for him to expel dark ones. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1294380/extras/pCutinPhilia.png?t=1732503360\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Philia the Human Cleric</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A cleric of the border sanctuary. She has a dream that one day everyone in the world can be equal. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1294380/extras/pCutinVenom.png?t=1732503360\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Venom the Dark Elf Ranger</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A dark elf who specializes in swordplay and archery. His close friend was killed by the Hero. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1294380/extras/pCutinCoyote.png?t=1732503360\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Coyote the Orc Defender</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A boy warrior from a tribe. He longed for the acceptance of humans and dark elves. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1294380/extras/pCutinSanguine.png?t=1732503360\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Sanguine the Reanimator</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A master of alchemy and necromancy. She is unscrupulous for her goals. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1294380/extras/pCutinBambooBlade.png?t=1732503360\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Bambooblade the Eastern Warrior</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The protagonist of MaouCat Studio's Dice and the Tower of the Reanimator: Glorious Princess. He comes from the Silver Kingdom in the Southeast.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Guidelines for Streams and Let's Plays</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">We are happy to have you stream our games or upload Let's Plays of them.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You may also monetize that gameplay, but only by using the features on online video platforms.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">We would appreciate it if you would include the game name in the stream or Let's Play title, or put the Steam page link in the description.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">We take no responsibility for any damage caused by your streams or Let's Plays.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">These guidelines are subject to change without notice.</p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Ending 1","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1294380/944e1a200bdbe4f71e8effbe45baba73af4b5bb9.jpg"},{"name":"Ending 2","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1294380/7609a84c75bb3e9ae580ff34f0b7a26d718df344.jpg"},{"name":"Ending 3","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1294380/fd960fc9382e42eeba390b88e2f1ed04c47bb47f.jpg"},{"name":"Ending 4","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1294380/e7092a8411345674484f2b379d7c20f548986e4b.jpg"},{"name":"Ending 5","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1294380/6d78d2e1771e437be97a161e41edf2dec37db089.jpg"},{"name":"New Game Plus","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1294380/23d14a5b5d35f3b37381bf7a4e3bc1aa3e423716.jpg"},{"name":"Human Adventurer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1294380/6a52e13986bfa30fb396bdc55571213da1c54169.jpg"},{"name":"Dark Elf Adventurer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1294380/6de5e7ef89ce2a37492187f96ece5e06cb01ecef.jpg"},{"name":"Orc Adventurer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1294380/93f059a2c4d3f2916a0e0713fb7fcc2a43350b41.jpg"},{"name":"Goblin Killer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1294380/f2df8abe9c84d6923e90b9d258d3dc23d1b161a1.jpg"}],"total":24},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.co